{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/01-HUMANITY_Commands_01.gif?t=1724972507\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/shiba_icon.png?t=1724972507\" /> <strong>WORK LIKE A DOG</strong><br>HUMANITY is a third-person puzzle-action game where you become a dog to command massive, marching crowds of people to jump, turn, push, float, shoot, and climb their way to salvation across 90 story-mode stages.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/02-HUMANITY_Jump-Arc_01.gif?t=1724972507\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/03-HUMANITY_Level-Overview.gif?t=1724972507\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/shiba_icon.png?t=1724972507\" /> <strong>READY, AND\u2026ACTION!</strong><br>Devious puzzles and strategic thinking is broken up with more action-focused elements and platformer-like levels, even some epic boss battles!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/04-HUMANITY_Yellow-Core_01.gif?t=1724972507\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/shiba_icon.png?t=1724972507\" /> <strong>UGC = USER GENERATED CONTENT, UNLIMITED GRATIFYING CHALLENGES</strong><br>Browse an ever-growing library of stages created by other players. Play, rate, and discover new types of puzzles in this limitless vault.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/05-HUMANITY_userstages.gif?t=1724972507\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/shiba_icon.png?t=1724972507\" /> <strong>CREATE AND SHARE LEVELS</strong><br>Bring your ideas to life using the intuitive Stage Creator, be it a straightforward puzzle, action stage, or heck, even an artful sculpture!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581480/extras/shiba_icon.png?t=1724972507\" /> <strong>(OPTIONAL) VR Compatible</strong><br>Immerse yourself like never before as you tower over the teeming, ant-like people! Mu ha ha ha ha!<br><br>Whether on your standard display or in the optional VR Mode, watch as breathtaking swarms of people follow your commands to the exit, all in HUMANITY\u2019s stark iconic style, courtesy of director and celebrated visual designer Yugo Nakamura and famed game creator Tetsuya Mizuguchi (Rez Infinite, Tetris Effect: Connected).","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"WHO'S A GOOD BOY?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/725a3ae872817e1180605354aeb8e5f284bb0212.jpg"},{"name":"UP, UP, AND AWAY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/2180d0af110328ad0d36512c6f31932a9ccf7ca4.jpg"},{"name":"GOLDY, MINE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/c94582ae743ddd4b5934cf6d7ddd81432ea03e2d.jpg"},{"name":"PROLOGUE: IN THE BOOKS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/8535af0cd8eb91e1c936f2328aad552243e1317e.jpg"},{"name":"SCENIC ROUTE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/4b920b27f8071499070d2aed366a4a42c98223c7.jpg"},{"name":"AWAKENING: PUT TO BED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/28f2adaa63e2773920d88aeabafcc93684086fcc.jpg"},{"name":"CHOICE: MADE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1581480/4c46